As the contents of this page no longer exist in Old School RuneScape, this article is preserved for historical purposes.
This item cannot be obtained legitimately.
Big bucket of frozen camel milk can only be acquired through illegitimate means. The Old School RuneScape Wiki does not condone rule-breaking actions.

Big bucket of frozen camel milk is an item obtained during the 2022 Easter event. It is only seen by players during a cutscene where Phoebe Kay freezes the big bucket of camel milk outside Ferox Enclave.

Phoebe Kay casts a freezing spell that would freeze the camel milk (as well as kill Xi_plzPetDogz_xiX).
